# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Meta-repo .gitignore (the "beacon" front-door repo).
# The three code repos (backend/, dashboard/, Mobile app/) are SEPARATE git repos
# published on their own — they are excluded here so the meta repo does not embed
# them. The meta repo carries only the front-door docs: README, LICENSE, SECURITY,
# CONTRIBUTING, and the publishable docs/.
# See docs/PUBLISH-CHECKLIST.md (INTERNAL) for the full publication runbook.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# --- Independent code repos (published separately) ---
/backend/
/dashboard/
/Mobile app/

# --- NEVER publish: internal harness, working docs, challenge IP, 3rd-party assets ---
/.claude/
/.vscode/
/SUBMISSION-PLAN.md
/submission/
/docs/PUBLISH-CHECKLIST.md
/requirements/
/UNDP design/

# --- ML working dir (provenance is published via Mobile app/ml/ + bundled models) ---
/ml/

# --- Marketing / heavy media (keep out of the code/docs front door) ---
*.mp4
/damage-picture.png
/damage-picture.jpeg
/test-shots/

# --- OS / editor cruft ---
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
*.swp
.idea/
